data.description: Beautifully remodeled 2 bedroom home ready for it's new owners! Walk into this one story floor plan and you're greeted with beautiful original hardwood floors and all the charm that a old house has to offer! Close to all the amenities that Huntington and Barboursville have to offer. New windows, heating & air system, electrical service, hardwood floors redone, kitchen appliances, bathroom and kitchen in 2021. Roof is 5 years old. New deck and asphalt driveway outback as well! This home is turn key and ready for you to move in!
